(10)‘Operating system’ means a system software which controls the basic functions of the hardware or software and enables software applications to run on it;
(11)‘Cloud computing services’ means a digital service as defined in point 19 of Article 4 of Directive (EU) 2016/1148 of the European Parliament and of the Council 41 ;
